tan de repente ( suddenly ) is a 2002 argentine and dutch black-and-white comedy drama film directed by diego lerman and written by lerman , maría meira , and eloisa solaas , based on the novel la prueba , written by césar aira . the drama features tatiana saphir , carla crespo , veronica hassan , among others . a young , naive clerk at a lingerie store learns about love and her own identity .